org.apache.beam.runners.fnexecution.control

Class SdkHarnessClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.runners.fnexecution.control.SdkHarnessClient

  • public class SdkHarnessClient
extends java.lang.Object
    A high-level client for an SDK harness.

    This provides a Java-friendly wrapper around FnApiControlClient and CloseableFnDataReceiver, which handle lower-level gRPC message wrangling.
